hadiths[80]{hadithnumber,text}:
2615,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din logon mein sab sey pehley khoon key muqaddamat key faisley hongey."
2616,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis insan ko bhi zulm key tor par qatl kya jata hai uskey khoon (key gunah) ka eik hissey Adam (Alaihissalam) key pehley betey (Qaabeel) ko bhi milta hai. kyonkey sab sey pehley usney qatl ka tariqa jaari kya."
2617,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din logon mein sab sey pehley khoon key muqaddamaat key faisley hongey."
2618,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Johni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah sey is haal mein milta hai ke uskey sath kisi chiz ko (ibadat mein) shareek nahin karta aur kisi haram khoon mein mulawwis nahin hota to wo jannat mein dakhil ho jata hai."
2619,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki nazar mein kisi momin ko nahaq qatl karney sey puri duniya ka tabah ho jana bhi kam ahmiyat rakhta hai."
2620,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney kisi momin key qatl mein aadhey lafz key sath bhi taawun kya, wo jab Allah sey milega to uski peshani par likha hoga : Allah ki rehmat sey mayus."
2621,"Hazrat Salim bin Abu-Ja'ad (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey puchha gaya ke us shakhs ka kya hukm hai jisney kisi momin ko jan-bujh kar qatl kar diya, phir tauba kar li , eman laya , nek aamal kiye aur hidayat ikhtiyar ki ? Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : afsos ! usey hidayat kahan mil sakti hai? mainey tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : qiyamat key din qatil is haal mein hazir hoga ke maqtool ney uska sar pakad rakha hoga aur wo kaheyga : ya rab ! is sey poochh, isney mujhey kyon qatl kya ? Allah ki qism ! Allah ney wo aayat tumharey Nabi par nazil farmaai , phir nazil farmaney key baad mansookh nahin ki."
2622,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai, unhoney farmaya : kya main tum ko eik hadees na sunaaun jo mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key dahane-Mubarak sey suni hai? usey mainey khud apney kanon sey suna , aur merey dil ney usey yad rakha.) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik bandey ney ninnanwey insan qatl kiye . aakhir usey tauba ka khayal aa gaya, chunanche usney duniya key sab sey badey aalim key barey mein daryaft kya to usey eik aadmi ka pata diya gaya . wo uskey paas gaya aur kaha : main ninnanwey insan qatl kar chuka hun . kya meri tauba mumkin hai? usney kaha : ninnanwey insan ( qatl kerney) key baad (tauba ka tariqa poochhtey ho?) usney talwaar nikal kar usey bhi qatl kar diya aur so ki tadaad puri kar di . uskey baad phir tauba ki khahish paida hui to usney duniya key sab sey badey aalim key barey mein daryaft kya. usey eik aadmi ka pata diya gaya, chunanche wo uskey paas gaya aur kaha : mainey so afrad ko qatl kya hai to kya meri tauba mumkin hai? usney kaha : tera bhala ho ! terey aur tauba key darmiyan kon rukawat bin sakta hai? to jis gandi basti mein rihaaish pazeer hai usey chhod kar nek logon ki falan basti mein chala ja aur wahan apney rab ki ibadat kar. wo nek logon ki basti mein janey key iraday sey (apni basti sey) nikal khada huwa . raastey mein usey maut aa gaee . uskey barey mein rehmat key farishton aur azab key farishton mein ikhtilaf ho gaya . iblees ney kaha : uska mujh sey gehra talluq hai. usney eik ghadi bhi meri nafarmani nahin ki. rehmat key farishton ney kaha : ye taaib ho kar ghar sey nikla hai. ( hadees key Raavi) Hamaam bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Humed Tawil ney Bakr bin Abdullah sey , unhoney Hazrat abu-Raafey (Rahimahullah) sey bayan kya, wo farmatey hain : Allah azz-w-jall ney eik farishta bheja . un farishton ( ki dono jamaaton) ney uskey samney maamla pesh kya aur uski taraf ruju kya. usney kaha : dekho , ye aadmi dono bastiyon mein sey kis key ziyada qarib tha, usey us basti walon mein shamil kar lo . Hazrat Imam Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : usey jab maut aai thi to wo ( martey martey bhi) ghisat kar nek logon ki basti sey qarib huwa , aur burey logon ki basti sey door huwa , chunanche farishton ney isey nek basti walon mein shumar kar liya . Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney eik dusri sanad sey Hamaam key wastey sey ye riwayat isi tarah bayan ki hai."
2623,"Hazrat abu-Shuraih ( khuwelid bin Amr) Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisko qatl ya zakham ki musibat pahunchey to usey teen chizon mein sey eik ko ikhtiyar karney ka haq hasil hai. agar wo chauthi chiz hasil karna chahey to uskey haath pakad lo (mana kar do) wo (qisaas key tor par mujrim ko) qatl kar ley, ya maaf kar dey, ya diyat wasul kar ley. jisney un mein sey koi kaam kya, phir doosra kaam bhi kar diya to uskey liye jahannam ki aag hai, is mein wo hamesha hamesha rahega ."
2624,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis ka koi ( qaribi rishtedar) aadmi qatl ho jaey to usey do eik jaisi chizon mein sey eik key intikhaab ka haq hasil hai. ya (qatil ko) qatl kar ley, ya fidya ( diyat ) ley ley ."
2625,"Hazrat ziyada bin Saad bin zameera (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mujhey merey walid (Hazrat Saad bin zameera (Raziallahu anhu)) aur merey chacha ney hadees sunai . ye dono hazraat Hunain ki jang mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath hazir they, un dono ney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Zohar ki namaz padhaai, phir eik darkht key nichey beth gaey. qabila khandaf key sardar Hazrat Aqraa bin Habis (Raziallahu anhu) uth kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur Mohlim bin Jisama key qatl key barey mein guftgu karney lagey. Hazrat Uena bin Hisn (Raziallahu anhu) bhi khidmat mein hazir ho kar qabila Ashja key fard Aamir bin Azbat key qisaas ka mutalba karney lagey . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen farmaya : kya tum diyat (khoon baha) leney par razi ho? unhoney inkar kya. qabila banu Les ka eik aadmi jisey Muketal kehtey they, usney uth kar arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki qasam! main to Islam key shuru zamaney key us maqtool ki misal is tarah samajhta hun jaisey bakriyon ka rewad pani peeney aaya, us ko kankar maara gaya to rewad ka pichhla hissa bhag utha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhen hamarey us safar mein pachas oont mil jaeyngey aur pachas wapsi par mil jaeyngey. is par un logon ney diyat lena manzoor kar liya."
2626,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib ney apney walid sey aur unhoney apney dada Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat ki ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney jaan-bujh kar qatl kya, usey maqtool key warison key hawaley kar diya jaeyga, wo chahen to (qisaas key tor par) qatl kar den, chahen to diyat ley lein. aur diyat ki miqdaar teen saala tees oontniyaan, aur chaar saala tees oontniyaan aur chaalis hamila oontniyaan (kul tadaad so) hai. ye qatle-amad ki diyat hai. agar (us sey kam) kisi miqdaar par suleh ho jaey to unhen uska haq hasil hai. aur ye sakht (mughalliza) diyat hai."
2627,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghalati sey ho janey wala jo qatl, iraade ke saath kiye janey waley qatl key mushabeh ho, yani kodey ya dandey (ki zarab) sey qatl ho jaey (usko diyat) so oont hain. un mein sey chaalis hamila oontniyan hongi jinkey peton mein bachey hon. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney apney doosrey ustaad Muhammad bin Yahya ki sanad sey ye riwayat isi tarah bayan ki hai aur Qasim aur Abdullah bin Amr key darmiyan Aqba bin Aus ka wasta bayan kya hai."
2628,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Fateh Makka key din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Kaba ki seedhi par khadey huye, Allah ki hamd o sana bayan ki, phir farmaya : tamam tareefen us Allah key liye hain jisney apna wada pura kya, apney bandey ki madad ki, aur usi akeley ney ( dushmanon ki) tamam jamaaton ko shikast di. suno! qatle-khata ki surat mein, yani kodey aur lathi sey marney waley ki diyat (khoon baha) so oont hain. un mein sey chaalis hamila oontniyan hongi jinkey peton mein bachey hon. suno! daure-jahiliyat mein jo bhi cheezen qabile-fakhr samjhi jati thin aur jahiliyat mein waqey honey waley khoon, (wo sab) merey un do qadmon key nichey hain, siwaye Kaba shareef ki khidmat aur hajiyon ko pani pilaney key mansab key. main unhen unkey zimmedaaron key liye isi tarah qaaim rakhta hun jis tarah wo pehley sey chaley aa rahey hain."
2629,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney diyat ki miqdaar baara hazar (dirham) muqarrar farmaai.
2630,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs ghalati sey qatl ho jaey uski diyat tees binte-makhaz (eik saala oontniyaan), teen binte-labun (do saala oontniyaan), tees hiqqey (teen saala oontniyaan) aur das ibne-labun (do saala oont hain). Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) shehar walon key liye uska andaza chaar so Dinar ya uski barabar qeemat chaandi muqarrar farmatey they. naqad raqam ka ye taayun oonton (key mahnge ya sastey honey) key zamaney key mutabiq hota tha. jab oont mahnge hotey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un ki qeemat ( diyat ki naqad raqam) mein izafa farma detey . aur jab sastey ho jatey to un ki qeemat (ki muqarrara miqdaar) mein kami kar detey, us waqt jaisi bhi keyfiyat hoti (uskey mutabiq faisla farma detey.) , chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein unki qeemat chaar so aur aath so Dinar key darmiyan rahi, ya uskey barabar chaandi, yani aath hazar dirham, aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye faisla farmaya ke jis shakhs ki diyat gaayon waley key zimmey gaayon mein (wajibul-ada) ho to do so gayen (ada ki jaeyn) aur jis shakhs ki diyat bakriyon walon key zimmey bakriyon mein (wajibul-ada) ho to (uski diyat key tor par) do hazar bakriyan ada ki jaeyn ."
2631,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qatl khata ki diyat bees hiqqey ( teen saala oontniyaan), bees Jizey (chaar saala oontniyaan), bees binte-makhaz (eik saala oontniyaan), bees binte-labun (do saala oontniyaan) aur bees muzakkar ibne-makhaz (eik saala oont) hain."
2632,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney diyat ki miqdaar baara hazar ( dirham) muqarrar farmaai . ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : Allah Taala key us farman ka yehi matlab hai : ( وَمَا نَقَمُوا إِلَّا أَنْ أَغْنَاهُمُ اللَّهُ وَرَسُولُهُ مِنْ فَضْلِهِ )' ye sirf is baat sey naraz ho rahey hain ke unhen Allah ney apney Fazal sey aur uskey Rasool ney dolat mand kar diya . Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : yani unhoney diyat wasul ki (aur is tarah dolat mand ho gaey uskey baad bajaey shukr guzari ka raasta ikhtiyar karney key musalmanon key khilaf sazishen aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki shaan mein gustakhi ka raasta ikhtiyar kya.)
2633,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla diya ke diyat ki zimmey daar , aaqila (qatil ki biradari) hai."
2634,"Hazrat Miqdam (bin Madikarb) shaami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis ka koi waris nahin, uska mein waris hun . main uski diyat dunga aur uski wirasat lunga. aur jis ka koi waris nahin, mamu uska waris hai. wo uski diyat dega aur uski virasat lega."
2635,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney andha dhund ladaai mein , ya asbiyat ki bina par pathar, koda ya danda maar kar qatl kar diya, usey qatl khata ki diyat ada kerni padeygi, aur jisney jaan-bujh kar qatl kya, us sey qisaas liya jaeyga. aur jo koi qisaas leney mein rukawat baney is par Allah ki, farishton ki aur tamam logon ki lanat hai. uska koi farz ya nafl amal qubul nahin hoga ."
2636,"Hazrat Namran bin Jaariya (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat jaariya bin zafar (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke eik aadmi ney doosrey ki kalaai par talwaar maar kar jod key ilawa dusri jagah sey bazu kaat diya. usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey shikayat ki. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey diyat dilwaney ka hukm dey diya. usney kaha : Allah key Rasool! main to qisaas lena chahta hun. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : diyat ley ley, Allah tujhey barkat ata farmaai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey liye qisaas ka faisla na diya."
2637,"Hazrat Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dimagh ki jhilli tak pahunch janey waley zakham ka qisaas nahin, na jism key andruni khala (maslan pet) tak pahunch janey waley zakham mein aur na haddi ko apni jagah sey hata deney wali chot mein qisaas hai."
2638,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat abu-Jahm bin Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ko zakat wasul karney key liye bheja . eik aadmi zakat key barey mein un sey lad pada. abu-Jahm (Raziallahu anhu) ney isey maara to usey (sar ya chehrey par) zakham aa gaya. un logon ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! qisaas dilwaiye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhen itni-itni raqam (diyat key tor par) milegi. wo na maaney, aap ney (raqam mein izafa kar key) farmaya : tumhen itni-itni raqam milegi. to wo maan gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main logon mein khutba dey kar (aam aelan kar key) tumhari raza-mandi ki ittilaa dey dun? unhoney kaha : ji haan . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khutba diya aur farmaya : banu Les qabiley key ye hazraat merey paas qisaas leney key liye aaye they. mainey unhen itni itni raqam (diyat) ki peshkash ki hai. kya tum log razi ho? unhoney kaha : ji nahin. muhajrin ney un logon ko sarzanish karney ka irada kya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen ruk janey ka hukm diya, chunanche wo ruk gaey . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen ( dobara ( talab farma kar) diyat ki miqdaar mein) izafa farma diya, aur farmaya : kya tum razi ho? unhoney kaha : ji haan . aap ney farmaya : main logon mein khutba dey kar tumhari raza-mandi ki ittilaa dey raha hun . unhoney kaha : theek hai. tab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khutba diya, phir ( sab logon key samney un sey) farmaya : kya tum razi ho? unhoney kaha ji haan . Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mainey Muhammad bin Yahya sey suna , wo farma rahey they : is riwayat ko sirf Maamar ney bayan kya hai. unkey ilawa kisi sey ye riwayat mujhey malum nahin."
2639,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Janeen (pet key bachey) key qatl ki surat main eik ghulam ya londi deney ka faisla diya. jiskey khilaf faisla huwa tha, usney kaha : kya hum uski diyat den jisney piya, na khaya, cheekha na chillaya, aisa to kal-adam hota hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to shaairon wali baaten karta hai. uski diyat eik ghulam ya eik londi hai."
2640,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (bin Naufal) (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney aurat ka hamal saaqit ho janey key barey mein logon (Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum) sey mashwara kya to Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney meri mojudgi mein is qism key muqaddmey main eik ghulam ya eik londi ada karney ka faisla sadir farmaya tha. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : koi aadmi hazir karo jo tumharey sath gawahi dey , chunanche Hazrat Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi unkey sath gawahi di ."
2641,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney (logon sey) us mamley mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka faisla daryaft farmaya , yani pet key bachchey key qatl key mamley mein. Hazrat Hamal bin Malik bin Naabgha (Raziallahu anhu) ney uth kar kaha : meri do biwiyan thin, un mein sey eik ney dusri ko khemey ki lakdi maari, (is tarah) usey bhi qatl kar diya aur uskey pet key bachchey ko bhi qatl kar diya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney pet key bachchey ki diyat eik ghulam dilwaaee aur hukm diya ke us aurat ko (qisaas key tor par) qatl kar diya jaey."
2642,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they : diyat aaqila ko milegi , aur aurat ko apney khawind ki diyat (khoon baha) sey tarkey wala hissa nahin milega yahan tak key Hazrat Zahaak bin Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhen khat likh kar bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Ashim Zibabi (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi ko uskey khawind ki diyat sey tarka dilwaya tha. (tab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney ruju farma liya)."
2643,Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Hamal bin Malik Hazli (Raziallahu anhu) ko un ki us biwi key tarkey (viraasat) sey hissa dilwaya jisey un ki dusri biwi ney qatl kar diya tha.
2644,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib (Rahimahullah) ney apney walid sey , aur unhoney apney dada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat ki ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye faisla sadir farmaya ke ehle-kitab ka khoon-bahaa musalmanon key khoon-bahaa sey nisf (aadha) hai. ehle-kitab sey murad Yahudi aur Esai hain."
2645,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qatil waris nahin hota."
2646,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke banu Mudlij qabiley key eik aadmi abu-Qatada ney apney betey ko qatl kar diya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney us sey sau oontniyaan wasul kar leen. tees hiqqey (teen saala oontniyaan) tees jaz'ey (chaar saala oontniyaan) aur chaalis hamila oontniyaan. phir farmaya : maqtool ka bhai kahan hai? mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna hai : qatil key liye koi meeras nahin hai.
2647,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye faisla sadir (jaari) farmaya ke aurat ki diyat uskey usba rishtedar ada kerengey, wo jo bhi hon. aur unhen diyat mein sey tarkey key tor par kuchh nahin milega magar wohi jo uskey (as-haabul- furuz) warison sey bach jaey. aur agar aurat qatl ho jaey to uski diyat uskey warison key darmiyan (tarkey key tor par) taqseem hogi. wohi aurat key qatil ko qatl kar saktey hain."
2648,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney diyat, qatl karney wali aurat key usba rishte-daaron key zimmey dali. maqtool aurat key usba rishte-daaron ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! uska tarka hamein milega? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin, uska tarka uskey khawind aur uskey bachchon key liye hai."
2649,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki phuphi Hazrat Rubayee binte Nazar‬ (Raziallahu anha) ney eik ladki ka daant tod diya. unhon (Hazrat Rubayee key ghar walon) ney maaf kar deney ki darkhaast ki, lekin unhoney (doosre fariq ney maaf karney sey) inkar kar diya. unhoney diyat ada karney ki peshkash ki to unhoney (diyat qubul karney sey bhi) inkar kar diya. wo log (fareeqain) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qisaas ka hukm dey diya. Hazrat Anas bin Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya (meri behan) Rubayee (Raziallahu anha) ka daant tod diya jaeyga? qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko sacha Deen dey kar bheja hai ! uska daant nahin toda jaeyga. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Anas ! Allah ka qanoon to qisaas hi hai. (Raavi ney kaha : ) phir wo log razi ho gaey aur unhoney maaf kar diya. tab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ka koi banda aisa bhi hota hai jo Allah par (aitimaad kartey huye) qism kha ley to Allah Taala uski qism puri farma deta hai."
2650,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab daant barabar hain. samney ka daant aur daadh barabar hain."
2651,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney daant key barey mein paanch oonton ka faisla farmaya.
2652,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye aur ye barabar hain. yani chhoti ungli , (chhoti key sath wali ungli) aur angoothaa (sab barabar hain)."
2653,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ungliyan sab (aapas mein) barabar hain. un ki diyat das das oont hai."
2654,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ungliyan barabar hain."
2655,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jin zakhmon sey haddi zahir ho jaey, un mein paanch paanch oont diyat hai."
2656,"Hazrat Yala bin Umayya aur Hazrat Salma bin Umayya sey riwayat hai, un dono ney farmaya : ghazwaae-tabuk mein hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath rawana huye. hamarey sath hamara eik dost tha. raastey mein uski eik aadmi sey ladaai ho gaee. aadmi ney apney sathi key haath par daant sey kaat liya, saathi ney uskey munh sey apna haath khincha to uska samney ka daant toot gaya. wo apney daant ki diyat leney key liye Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik aadmi apney bhai ka haath is tarah chabaataa hai jis tarah oont (kisi ka haath) chabaa jata hai, phir diyat maangney aa jata hai. is daant ki koi diyat nahin. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey daant ko diyat ka haq na rakhney wala qarar dey diya."
2657,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney doosrey key bazu par daant sey kaat liya. usney apna haath khincha to kaatney waley ka daant toot kar gir gaya. ye muqadma Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kya gaya to aap ney uskey daant ko diyat ka haq na rakhney wala qarar dey diya. aur farmaya : tum mein sey koi aisey kaatna hai jaisey oont kaat khata hai.
2658,"Hazrat abu-Juhaifa Wahab bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : kya aap logon key paas koi aisa ilm hai jo (doosrey) logon key paas nahin? unhoney kaha : nahin, qism hai Allah ki ! hamarey paas to wohi kuch hai jo logon key paas hai, siwaye iskey ke Allah Taala kisi aadmi ko Quran ki samajh ata farma dey, ya jo us nawishtey mein hai. us tehreer mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key farmaaey huye diyat key masaayel they, aur ye (likha huwa tha) ke musalman ko kafir key badley mein qatl na kya jaey."
2659,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman ko kafir key badley mein qatl nahin kya jaeyga."
2660,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin ko kafir key badley mein qatl na kya jaey aur na ehad waley (zimmi) ko uskey ehad mein qatl kya jaey ."
2661,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : betey key badley mein baap ko qatl na kya jaey."
2662,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : baap ko aulad key badley mein qatl na kya jaey ."
2663,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney apney ghulam ko qatl kya, hum usey qatl kar dengey, aur jisney ghulam key naak kaan kaatey , hum bhi uskey naak kaan kaat dengey."
2664,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi ney jaan-boojh kar apney ghulam ko amadan qatl kar diya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney usey so kodey lagwaaey, usey eik saal key liye jala watan kar diya aur musalmanon (key maale-ghanimat) mein sey uska hissa khatam kar diya ."
2665,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi ney eik aurat ka sar do patharon key darmiyan kuchal kar usey qatl kar diya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bhi us (qatil) ka sar do patharon key darmiyan kuchal diya .
2666,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi ney eik ladki ko uskey chaandi key zewaron key liye qatl kar diya. (abhi faut nahin hui thi ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir kar di gaee.) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey farmaya : kya tujhey falan aadmi ney qatl kya hai? usney sar sey ishara kya ke nahin, phir dobara ( kisi aur ka naam ley kar) puchha to usney ishara kya ke nahin . teesri baar (us Yahudi ka naam ley kar) puchha to usney sar sey ishara kya ke haan. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us (mujrim) ko do patharon key darmiyan ( sar kuchal kar) qatl karwa diya ."
2667,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qisaas sirf talwaar sey hota hai."
2668,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qisaas sirf talwaar sey hota hai."
2669,"Hazrat Amr bin Ahwas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey hajjatul-wadaa mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : suno ! koi jurm karney wala apney siwa kisi par jurm nahin karta. na baap key jurm ki zimmey daari uskey betey par hai, na betey key jurm ki zimmey daari uskey baap par hai."
2670,"Hazrat Tariq Mahaaribi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haath buland farmaaey yahan tak key mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baghlon ki safedi nazar aai. aap ney farmaya : suno! kisi maa key jurm ki zimme-daari uskey betey par nahin. suno! kisi maa key jurm ki zimme-daari uskey betey par nahin ."
2671,"Hazrat Khaskhaash Anbari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa, aur merey sath mera beta tha, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : terey jurm ki puchhgachh ussey nahin hogi aur uskey jurm ki puchhgachh tujh sey nahin hogi."
2672,"Hazrat Usama bin Shareek (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi jaan key jurm ki zimmey daari dusri jaan par nahin."
2673,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chopaey ka pahunchaya huwa zakham rayegaan hai. aur kaan (mein gir kar aaney wala zakham) rayegaan hai aur kunwaan rayegaan hai. ,"
2674,"Hazrat Amr bin Auf Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna : janwer ka pahunchaya huwa zakham rayegaan hai, aur kaan rayegaan hai."
2675,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye faisla farmaya ke kaan rayegaan hai, kunwaan rayegaan hai, aur chopaey ka pahunchaya huwa zakham rayegaan hai. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Ajmaa sey murad maweshi waghera janwer hain. aur jabbaar, yani rayegaan, wo hota hai jiska koi tawaan (ya diyat waghera) na ho."
2676,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aag rayegaan hai aur kunwaan rayegaan hai."
2677,"Hazrat Sehal bin abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) apney qabiley key buzurgon sey riwayat kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Mahisa (Raziallahu anhu) tang dasti ki wajeh sey (rozi ki talash mein) khaibar gaey. (wahan) kisi ney aa kar Mahisa (Raziallahu anhu) ko bataya ke Abdullah bin Sehal ko qatl karkey khaibar key eik kunwen ya chashmey mein phenk diya gaya hai. Mahisa (Raziallahu anhu) ney yahudiyon key paas ja kar unhen kaha : qism hai Allah ki! tumhii ney isey qatl kya hai. unhoney kaha : qism hai Allah ki ! hamney isey qatl nahin kya. phir wo (khaibar sey) apney qabiley walon key paas gaey aur unhen soorate-hal batai, phir Mahisa (Raziallahu anhu) apney badey bhai huwesa (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) key sath (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein) hazir huye . Mahisa (Raziallahu anhu) ney baat shuru kerni chahi kyonkey (hadisey key waqt) khaibar mein wohi they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Mahisa (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : badey ka lihaz karo . yani jo umr mein bada hai (usey baat karney do.) chunanche Huwesa (Raziallahu anhu) ney baat ki, phir unkey baad Mahisa (Raziallahu anhu) ney baat ki. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ya wo tumharey maqtool ki diyat den ya jang key liye tayyar ho jaeyn. chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us mamley mein ehal khaibar key naam likha. unhoney (jawab mein) likha , qism hai Allah ki! hamney isey qatl nahin kya. tab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Huwesa, Mahisa aur Abdur-Rehman Raziallahu anhum sey farmaya : kya tum qasmen khatey ho aur apney aadmi (maqtool) ka khoon baha (diyat) leney key mustahiq bantey ho? unhoney kaha : ji nahin. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir Yahudi tumharey liye qasmen khaeyngey (qasmen kha kar khud ko be gunah Sabit kar dengey.) unhoney kaha : wo musalman nahin (un key liye jhooti qasmen khana maamuli baat hai.) chunanchey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney paas sey Abdullah bin Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ki diyat dey di, aur unkey paas so oontniyaan bhej din. aur wo unkey ghar pahuncha di gaeen. Hazrat Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : un mein sey eik surkh oontni ney mujhey laat bhi maari thi ."
2678,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Masood key betey Huwesa aur Mahisa (Raziallahu anhuma) aur Sehal key betey Abdullah aur Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhuma) ghalla leney khaibar gaey . (wahan) Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) par hamla kar key usey qatl kar diya gaya . ye maamla Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein arz kya gaya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum qasmen kha kar (diyat key) mustahiq bantey ho? unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! hum kaisey qism kha saktey hain jabke hamney dekha nahin? aap ney farmaya : phir Yahudi (qasmen kha kar) tum sey bari ho jaeyngey. unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool! tab to wo hamen qatl karna shuru kar dengey. wo jisey chahengey qatl kar key pachas jhooti qasmen kha liya kerengey. tab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney paas (baitul-maal) sey uski diyat ada farma di.
2679,"Hazrat Salma bin Rooh bin Zanbaa apney dada (Hazrat Zanbaa bin Rooh Juzaai (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye, unhoney apney ghulam ko khassi kar diya tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney musley ki wajeh sey us ghulam ko azad kar diya."
2680,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi cheekhta chillata Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tujhey kya huwa? usney kaha : merey aaqa ney mujhey uski eik londi ka bosa letey dekh liya to usney merey mardana aaza kaat daley. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is shakhs ko merey paas lao. usey talash kya gaya lekin wo pakda na ja saka to Rasulullah ney (ghulam sey) farmaya : ja, to azad hai. usney kaha : Allah key Rasool! meri madad kon kerega? Raavi ney kaha : uska matlab ye tha ke agar merey aaqa ney mujhey dobara ghulam bana liya to mujhey kon chhudaaeyga? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har momin, ya farmaya : har musalman (teri madad kerega)."
2681,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qatl karney key andaz mein bhi sab logon sey ziyada gunah sey bachney waley momin hi hotey hain."
2682,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin hi qatl karney key andaz mein bhi sab logon sey ziyada gunah sey bachney waley hotey hain."
2683,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalmanon key khoon baham (aapas mein) hum martaba hain. wo dusron (ghair Muslim dushmanon) key khilaf eik haath ki tarah hain. unka adnaa bhi muahidey ki zimmey daari utha sakta hai. musalmanon ko wo (Mujahid) bhi ghanimat ada kerega jo sab sey door (aur dushman sey bilkul qarib) hai."
2684,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman dusron key khilaf eik haath ki tarah hain. aur unkey khoon baham (aapas mein) barabar hain."
2685,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalmanon ka haath gheron key khilaf (eik hi) hota hai. unkey khoon aur maal (martabey aur qabile hifazat honey key lihaz sey) barabar hain. aur musalmanon key khilaf (kisi ghair Muslim ko) sab sey kam darjey ka musalman bhi panah dey sakta hai, aur musalmanon ko wo (Mujahid) bhi (ghanimat) ada kerega jo sab sey door hai."
2686,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi zimmi ko qatl karey usey jannat ki khushbu nahin aayegi, halanke uski khushbu chaalis saal key faasley sey mehsus hoti hai."
2687,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney kisi zimmi ko qatl kiya, jiski (hifazat ki) zimmey-daari Allah aur uskey Rasool ney uthai hai to wo jannat ki khushbu nahin paeyga, halanke uski khushbu sattar saal key faasley sey mehsus hoti hai."
2688,"Hazrat Rifaa bin Shaddad Qatbaani (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : agar mainey Hazrat Amr bin Haamiq Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) sey eik hadees na suni hoti to Mukhtaar Saqafi key sar aur dhad key darmiyan chalta (uska sar dhad sey alag kar deta). mainey Hazrat Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs sey koi apna khoon mehfooz samajhta ho aur wo usey qatl kar daley to qiyamat key din wo (qatil) ehad shikni (todne) ka jhandaa uthaey huye hoga."
2689,"Hazrat Rifaa (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Mukhtaar Saqafi key paas uskey mehal mein gaya. usney kaha : Jibril (Alaihissalam) abhi abhi merey paas sey uth kar gaey hain. main sirf isliye usey qatl na kar saka ke mainey Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Surd (Raziallahu anhu) sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ye hadees suni thi ke aap ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs tujh sey apney khoon key barey mein mutmain ho (usey yaqin ho ke uskey haath sey meri jaan mehfooz hai) to usey qatl na kar. isi (farman) ney mujhey is (ko qatl kerney) sey rok diya."
2690,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamana Mubarak main eik shakhs ney qatl kar diya. usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir kiya gaya to aap ney isey maqtool key waris key supurd kar diya. qatil ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! qism hai Allah ki ! mera usey qatl karney ka irada nahin tha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney maqtool key waris sey farmaya : suno ! agar wo sachcha huwa, phir bhi tum ney isey qatl kar diya to tum jahannam mein jaogey. usney isey azad kar diya. Raavi ney bayan kiya : uskey bazu chamdey ki rassi sey bandhey huye they. (uskey chhod deney par) wo rassi kheenchtaa huwa nikla, (isliye) usey zoo-nisaa (tasmey wala) kaha janey laga."
2691,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik shakhs apney wali (qaribi rishtedar) key qatil ko Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley aaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maaf kar do. usney inkar kar diya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khoone-bahaa ley lo. usney inkar kar diya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jaao, isey qatl kar do, tum bhi is jaisey ho. eik aadmi uskey peechhey ja kar usey mila aur usey bataya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : usey qatl kar do, tum bhi us jaisey ho. usney (fauran) usey chhod diya. Raavi kehtey hain : dekha gaya ke wo shakhs tasma (chamdey ki rassi) kheenchtaa huwa ghar ja raha tha. (Raavi key us lafz sey) malum hota hai ke maqtool key waris ney usey baandha huwa tha. Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Qasim (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key baad kisi ko ye kehney ka haq hasil nahin : usey qatl kar dey, to bhi us jaisa hai.  Imam Ibne-Maja ney farmaya : ye hadees Ramla walon ki hai. sirf unhoney riwayat ki hai."
2692,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney jab bhi koi aisa muqadma pesh kiya gaya jis mein qisaas hota to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney maaf karney ka hukm diya."
2693,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : jis ko jism mein koi takleef pahunchey, phir wo us (takleef pahunchaney waley) ko maaf kar dey to Allah Taala uski wajeh sey uska darja buland karta hai, aur uska gunah maaf karta hai. Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ye baat merey kanon ney suni aur merey dil ney isey yad rakha."
2694,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal, Hazrat Abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah , Hazrat Ubada bin Samit aur Hazrat Shaddad bin Aous‬ Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar aurat qatl jaan boojh kar karey aur wo hamila ho to usey (qisaas mein) qatl nahin kiya jaeyga yahan tak key uskey pet ka bachcha paida ho jaey aur yahan tak key wo kisi ko apney bachchey ki parwarish ki zimmey daari saunp dey. aur agar wo zina karey to usey rajm nahin kiya jaeyga yahan tak key uskey pet ka bachcha paida ho jaey aur yahan tak key wo kisi ko apney bachchey ki parwarish ki zimme-daari saunp dey."
